{"tid":2319652,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] PES MOBILE 2021 【325】 開住先啦屌","createTime":"2020-12-10T08:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T09:02:35.000Z","uid":199925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ac1514c99494427d83789ae0f5772312f3f97a11","tid":2319652,"uid":199925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/12/07/e/ef525ebc286dd9a054be4d02d8d1b0ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2Fe%2Fef525ebc286dd9a054be4d02d8d1b0ba.jpg&h=528a7b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niconic moment:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CzO3w4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCzO3w4e.jpg&h=e4f1d82c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n● 新手開波Q&amp;A?<br />\n<br />\n1. 洗唔洗刷首抽?<br />\n新手開波既時候會有好多抽，盡量黑波起手，coins留黎抽Fp(精選球員)，唔滿意既可以繼續刷到自己想要既球員為止。<br />\n<br />\n3. 點樣改Email或者密碼?<br />\n<a href=\"https://my.konami.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.konami.net%2F&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=c5582e21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://my.konami.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 操控方法<br />\n操控類型有 Advanced 同 Classic 揀<br />\n推薦 Classic 佢類似手制咁樣同埋易上手啲<br />\n<br />\n● 球員資料<br />\nPES DATABASE<br />\n<a href=\"http://pesdb.net/pes2020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpesdb.net%2Fpes2020%2F&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=d4caebb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pesdb.net/pes2020/</a><br />\n要注意由於可能有球員更新，所以DATABASE 入面既100%抽球員可能有誤。<br />\n<br />\n只需要直接search球員名，你就可以搵到該球員特性同數值。<br />\n而想搵一堆某類球員，可以憑Search Conditions自行set Filters 搵出黎。<br />\n<br />\n● 不同底色球員資料<br />\n紅色=強化版legend(非常難中)(使用該球會球衣有加乘)（球員會保留至下季）<br />\n金色=普通版legend<br />\n<br />\n紫色=強化版現役(現實比賽中表現良好的球員會出現係fp pool到)或club selection <br />\n藍色=普通版現役，跟隨現實球員表現，狀態會不同(可以3個黑波換一個)<br />\n灰色=舊版現役，狀態永遠C(2019版本或之前)<br />\n<br />\n●畫面調整<br />\n新手入game 第一件事畫質60 fps<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CeCsohL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCeCsohL.png&h=9f7ffdb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SLyWgCP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSLyWgCP.png&h=3d1ada1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但30fps low quality 比較慳電<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n●實時系統<br />\n每周四維護6小時（10am-4pm)後，會按照現實球員表現而調整球員狀態；<br />\n另有巴打 隨時更新球員實際操作表現（暗改），詳情要留意留言<br />\n<br />\n●教練更新<br />\n即日起，可簽入不同版本的同名教練。每日更新3次 (1000 1800 0200)，已擁有的教練不能再簽下<br />\n<br />\n●拍賣<br />\n根本球員條件（國籍，球會，年歲，能力）買球探組合球員<br />\n詳情：PES DATABASE<br />\n<a href=\"http://pesdb.net/pes2020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpesdb.net%2Fpes2020%2F&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=d4caebb4\" target=\"_blank\">http://pesdb.net/pes2020/</a><br />\n●賺取Gp方法<br />\n<br />\nOpen challenge ，打哂三關有75000gp<br />\n<br />\nMatchday ，除左部分比賽有coins外，每關夠1500積分，可以觀戰賺取gp<br />\n<br />\n季節賽掛tour(適宜新手)，以白銅銀波掛機，升班可以賺取23000~24000gp<br />\n<br />\n●遊戲玩法<br />\n<br />\nTour &amp;Tour Sim<br />\n用fp球員既%會高d (分數較高)<br />\n<br />\n最少打2500 points 賺導師(幫球員升lv)<br />\n<br />\ncampaign sim <br />\n<br />\n刷gp 用狀態A/B 銀波+白波bench(升班有23000gp~24000gp)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n●Matchday<br />\n<br />\n有coins既matchday 就打夠5500分<br />\n想刷gp可以繼續打 前300名可以參加比賽(抽籤)<br />\n無coins既matchday 打1500分就得 記得觀戰賺gp<br />\n<br />\n兩種玩法<br />\n<br />\nPreset team<br />\n使用該球會的藍底球員，不扣合約費<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nio69mb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNio69mb.jpg&h=67e7dcfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9BCjKUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9BCjKUD.jpg&h=8b21b409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自已球員代表球會出戰<br />\n自由選擇代表一個球會，使用該球會球員球隊值會更高，獲得更多積分，且狀態必定A<br />\n<br />\n球隊值：<br />\nlegend 或Fp 800％<br />\n藍底 480％<br />\n灰底 400％<br />\n敵對球員 50％<br />\n<br />\n例子（選擇國際米蘭）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HMNORUZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHMNORUZ.jpg&h=00df984f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Grhy21P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGrhy21P.jpg&h=003923f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/amsn2g0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Famsn2g0.jpg&h=8d0c6388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wio22ha.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwio22ha.jpg&h=ee46add3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電莖玩家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登杯冠軍名單<br />\n<br />\n2020UEFA: 月城雪兔<br />\n2020World cup: 出奧燒啦<br />\n2020歐洲x南美杯: 出奧燒啦<br />\n2500戰力杯: Aristo<br />\n第二屆普黑團體盃賽: Aristo 一生人三次 waiiiiiiii 我朋友係金毛獅王<br />\nLegend盃： 出奧燒啦、AC米蘭、 鳩改住先、球皇balotelli<br />\n歐國盃: AC 米蘭, 香港高登, 用住先啦<br />\n<br />\nPes mobile三巨頭<br />\n牛<br />\n兔<br />\n啤"},{"pid":"6f38275147a6356f8230015534835e007a7a412a","tid":2319652,"uid":50321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T08:55:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我呢個悲劇人物又準備出場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>傳啲運氣俾你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>想要馬圖斯，攻守都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n金底夠做，而且係 box to box <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cf3c35386af23e5b396969e16b6dd1af0c1a6b","tid":2319652,"uid":199925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T08:55:40.000Z","msg":"唔記得改數字 用住先開唔開返326"},{"pid":"5b6303bd62b53793e6d2c9bbfe42bbf9f4f0c430","tid":2319652,"uid":174940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/26HEL4q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F26HEL4q.png&h=c3d69d70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n路明首戰成碌柒咁 最後都係出Torres先入波  好後悔抽左咁多野"}]}